channel.title: MarioWebissä - Essence of Tranquility
channel.description:
DJ Mario Webissä is a Fresh New Name in the Electronic Dance Music Scene.
Brings you the best of Epic Trance Anthems from around the globe with a cheeky set of Trance populations and will get you down to the dance floor.
Essence of Tranquility in one of his Latest projects will bring you the best names in the Electronic Dance Music Industry.
If you want to show your support VOTE FOR DJ Mario Webissä in THE DJ LIST to enjoy the best of Trance Anthems to you’re inseparable i-pod.
Mario showcase all styles of dance music from around the world which features the best in Trance,Classics, Progressive,Vocal,Uplifting, psy.
Enjoy the show.
****************************************** Praise, hate, comments, suggestions and even your track requests are most welcome.
